{"tid":2297510,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美聯物業環球大廈總部同層有確診者 所有員工暫撤離","createTime":"2020-11-23T10:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T10:33:46.000Z","uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8776cf5fef30676f857fb81dffb69622363cc39d","tid":2297510,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:23:00.000Z","msg":"第四波疫情社區式蔓延，美聯物業設於中環環球大廈總部25樓同層的其他單位出現確診個案，該層今日會進行清潔消毒，美聯物業安排該層所有員工撤離，暫時在家工作，保障員工健康，明日才回復正常辦公。<br />\n<br />\n美聯物業向員工發通告，提醒同事不要到訪環球大廈總部25樓，員工可自行安排做病毒檢測，亦已通知外間機構人士暫停到訪。"},{"pid":"9b39dea030033c9c094923cd0ec1599691ff8087","tid":2297510,"uid":187741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:27:50.000Z","msg":"暫時在家工作，保障員工健康，明日才回復正常辦公。"},{"pid":"e4284c84fc2f9e4688cf66ada589ca9e20c1fd8e","tid":2297510,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b39dea030033c9c094923cd0ec1599691ff8087","tid":2297510,"uid":187741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:27:50.000Z","msg":"暫時在家工作，保障員工健康，明日才回復正常辦公。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:29:33.000Z","msg":"一日就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d9af1eadbec38a99046428d8bf6fe25f05c98c","tid":2297510,"uid":254976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4284c84fc2f9e4688cf66ada589ca9e20c1fd8e","tid":2297510,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b39dea030033c9c094923cd0ec1599691ff8087","tid":2297510,"uid":187741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:27:50.000Z","msg":"暫時在家工作，保障員工健康，明日才回復正常辦公。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:29:33.000Z","msg":"一日就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:33:46.000Z","msg":"都係做下樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}